How to setup Easy PHP Framework (EPF)

Step 1:
 - # cd [to your folder at your webroot, like /var/www/]
 - # git clone git://github.com/itarato/easy-php-framework.git
 
Step 3:
 - create a database
 
Step 4:
 - customize your database settings in setup.php at project root
 
Step 5:
 - make sure rewrite_mod enabled by apache2 (eg rewrite.load & AllowOverride All)
 
Step 6:
 - write your browsers search bar: localhost/easy-php-framework/
 
Requirements:
 - apache 2
 - php 5.2
 - mysql 5
 
More details at http://www.bison.hu

